Well, I woke up feeling lousy again.

But after a bit, my mom calls all like &quot;omigosh xDDDD we&#039;re down on 23rd :DDD come grab some pizza :))))) we got a whole pie, and it&#039;ll be cold by the time we get back :333333&quot;

And I&#039;m sitting here with nausea, all like &quot;kk brt xD&quot;

So I went for pizza with the folks, and as I ate, I could feel the pain. Every bit of it. Now we&#039;re home, and I&#039;m still in pain.

Why do I do this to myself?
